	if Statements:
		if else conditions allow us to write programs that can take decisions based 
		on some condition and provided data.
		-if condition
		-if else condition
		-if else if condition
		-nested if else condition
		
		Why we should learn about if else condition?
		Like testing a website our program needs to make a lot of decisions.
		
	What is the syntax of if else conditions?
	-if condition	
	
	boolean rich=true;
	if(rich){
	System.out.println("start writing as many codes inside the brackets");
	}
	